product_name: Omega Pacific 7/16'' Mod D Screw-Lok Carabiner - Steel
long_description: A must-have for every rescue kit, the industrial-strength Omega Pacific 7/16 in. Mod D Screw-Lok carabiner is one of the stronger 'biners available. Modified D-shape provides excellent handling for all-around use. Steel is heat treated and plated for superb corrosion resistance. Screw-Lok gate prevents accidental opening of gate during usage and operates well in all weather conditions.
